    * OS X: Fixed fullscreen windowing
    * OS X: Fixed dylib loading when DYLD_FALLBACK_LIBRARY_PATH is defined
    * Linux: Fixed exclusive mode problems when keyboard focus is lost
    * Linux: Support for bitmap fonts.

